        "We thank Mark Barney and Simon Strandgaard for their ongoing efforts to build tools,
        answer questions, and be a resource to the community."
      </blockquote>
      <cite class="text-xs text-muted mt-2 block not-italic">
        Source: <a href="https://arcprize.org/blog/arc-prize-2025-results-analysis" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                   class="text-accent-glow hover:underline">arcprize.org/blog/arc-prize-2025-results-analysis</a>
      </cite>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Table -->
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">GitHub Statistics</h2>
