      <h2 class="text-sm font-mono text-lobster uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">LODA Language Ecosystem</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-4">
        Simon co-created LODA, an assembly language for discovering integer sequences. He wrote the Rust implementation.
        Org: <a href="https://github.com/loda-lang" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent-glow hover:underline">github.com/loda-lang</a>
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-xs font-mono">
        {[
          { name: "loda-rust", stars: 30 },
          { name: "loda-cpp", stars: 28 },
          { name: "loda-programs", stars: 38 },
          { name: "loda-api", stars: "‚Äî" },
        ].map(r => (
          <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
            <p class="text-text-primary">{r.name}</p>
